<p>
	This bright blue candle with white and yellow hearts on the surface has a dark and sensual fragrance with calming oceanic overtones and a steamy, woody heart. With frankincense and vetivert essential oils, the candle has been blended with pure quality essential oils and burns for approximately 45 hours. When in use place the candle tin on a heat resistant surface. Ensure the candle is kept away from any flammable materials and do not move the candle whilst it is alight or whilst the wax is molten. Keep out of reach of children and pets. Do not leave a burning candle unattended. This candle is suitable for vegans.</p>
